<author>mạhr fạyz, mạhr fạyz</author>
<title>yswʿ hw ạlṭryq</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- (yswʿ hw ạlṭryq .. yswʿ ạ̉ʿẓm ṣdyq)2
 (yswʿ hw ạlbdạyẗ .. yswʿ hw ạlnhạyẗ)2
 (yswʿ hw ạlḥyạẗ)2
 1- (btdwr ʿ ạlṭryq .. fy zmạn mlyạn bḍyq)2
 (msjwn fy ạlhm lyh .. mạ tqwm ạuṣrkẖ ạ̹lyh)2
 2- (hrbạn wlḥd fyn .. ḥyrạn jwh ạlạ̉nyn)2
 (bynạdy ʿlyk tʿwd .. bḥnạn mn gẖyr ḥdwd)2
 3- (hạtʿysẖ m ạlsn kạm .. fy snyn mn gẖyr slạm)2
 (lạ ạlmạl ydyk ạ̉mạn .. wlạ ṣạḥb lyk ḍmạn)2
 4- (hạtʿysẖ mlywn ṭryq .. mḥtạr bynhm gẖryq)2
 (wtʿwd mlyạn jrạḥ .. tbky ʿly̱ ʿmr rạḥ)2
 5- (dy jrwḥk rạḥ tṭyb .. fy rjwʿk llṣlyb)2
 (fy ạlfrḥ hnạk tʿysẖ .. ạ̉bdyẗ mạtnthysẖ)2</lyrics>
</song>